    		CONSEQUENCES

    		think of what would happen if we sterilzed criminals!

    		think of what would happen if a woman didnt have the right to an abortion!


    		TRADITION

    		goldberg, etc

    			rights of all people in free governments

    		deeply rooted traditions


    	What aspects of the family are protected?

    		family, sex, PROCREATION:  skinner, griswold

