    	WHITE uses a consequentialist argument

    		the consequences are trivial

    		you're blocked from this one suburb here, with the people who say are your family

    		there's no profound loss or lfielong disability


    	We have some kind of fundamental right

    		they should apply SS

    		they don't

    		they use something more like an intermediate level

    			there's a desire to resolve traffic issues and overcrowding

    				this would work for RBR but not for SS

    				semi legit ends

    			the means serve the ends marginally at best

    				so the law fails this mixed test

    		if they broke out SS for every case involving a fundamental right to family, shit hits fan

